lidationPipe({ whitelist: true, transform: true }))\n   287\texport class ImGate
way implements OnGatewayConnection, OnGatewayDisconnect {\n   288\t  // ...\n   
289\t}\n   290\t```\n   291\t\n   292\t### Gateway 认证与 CORS 规范\n   293\t\n 
