ob\n    82\t```\n    83\t\n    84\t#### 技术要求\n    85\t- Socket.io Gateway：`
apps/api/src/modules/im/im.gateway.ts`。\n    86\t- 事件约定：\n    87\t  - Clie
nt → Server：`message:send`（`conversation_id`, `content`, `type`, `client_messa
